  ('optician-moex-02321', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關紀錄視力值的史奈倫分數（Snellen fraction）表示法 ，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["分子表示測試距離", "分母表示視標張開5分弧角的距離", "6/24 = 20/80", "分母越小表示能解析的視標越大"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
